00:23.000 --> 00:32.000
I would like to warn you that by the end of this part you will know a lot about the assessment of personnel.

00:32.000 --> 00:38.000
Therefore, the third part of the workbook contains rather complex tasks.

00:38.000 --> 00:47.000
You will not only have to answer the questions of a test-like nature and choose the correct answer from several given options.

